{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I would say that probably most of those were the ones who originally, after the war, went out via Cyprus and everything to Israel who were the fighters in the First Israeli War of Independence.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those people understood that politics are all very well for Switzerland, for Denmark, for England, where peace is reigning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when you deal with a gun, you can only handle it with a gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all nice words, assurances, don't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I come from that generation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, having gone back on the transport, there were some interesting anecdotes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We travelled practically on hourly or half-daily basis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We got off one train, because it stopped, and we had to find another one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And eventually we got to the place called Bamberg, in central Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember they took, in the middle of the day, away the engine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They commandeered it away, the American military.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So everybody got off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a coal train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were Yugoslavs and all nationalities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We all got off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a field with onions and potatoes, and there was a little creek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had a marvelous meal for a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyway, eventually, as we progressed downwards in Germany, I remember one night I was-- we got onto an oil-- you know, these big oil tanker carriers, they've got a big metal plate on the side.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I was thin enough, and so on, so I spent the whole night, while the train was traveling, behind that plate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I suppose, with normal thinking, it was crazy to do it, but one was quite sort of unafraid already of anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
